Conservative radio host and former Sacramento resident Rush Limbaugh, both on "The Rush Limbaugh Show" and in print, frequently mentions Rio Linda.
========,2,Sports and recreation.
Rio Linda is home to the Roy Hayer Memorial Race Track.
This track is noted as the first track that four-time NASCAR champion Jeff Gordon ever competed on.
Rio Linda hosts the northern terminus of the Sacramento Northern Bike Trail.
